Multiple geoms

Customization

ggplot(mpg, aes(x = displ, y = hwy)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_smooth() +
  labs(title = "Realtionship b/w engine size & MPG",
       x = "Highway MPG",
       y = "Engine Displacement (liters)") +
  theme_bw() +
  theme(text = element_text(size = 16))
## `geom_smooth()` using method = 'loess'
